$ PowerShell: the automatic variables $true and $false

`$true` and `$false` are constants that represent the two values of → Microsoft/dot-net/namespaces-classes/System/Boolean[`System.Boolean`], which accordingly is the *type* of these values:
code {
PS C:\> $true.GetType().FullName
System.Boolean
code }

sa:
  Other → Windows/PowerShell/language/variable/automatic[automatic variables]
